(84, 2, 'Canon IXY 420F', '&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;Thông số kỹ thuật&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Độ phân giải : 16.1 Megapixels&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Cảm biến : 1/2.3&quot; CMOS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Zoom quang : 5x (35 -120mm)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Zoom kĩ thuật số : 4x&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Định dạng tập tin : JPEG (EXIF 2.2) , AVI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ ISO : Tự động, ISO 100 / 200 / 400 / 800 / 1600 / 3200 (khi ở chế độ P)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Màn hình LCD : 3.0&quot; TFT (460.000 pixels)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Thẻ nhớ: SD, SDHC, SDXC&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Quay phim: HD 1280 x 720, 640 x 480, 30fps/30fps(LP)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Chế độ tự động chụp: 2 hay 10 giây&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Khẩu độ: F2.0 – F5.3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Tốc độ chụp nhanh nhất: 1 - 1/2000 giây, 15-1/2000 giây&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Phạm vi đèn flash: 50cm - 4,0m (W), 50cm - 2,0m (T)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Canh nét gần: 3 cm&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Chống mắt đỏ, chống rung quang học, chế độ nhận dạng khuôn mặt&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;+ Chuẩn kết nối : USB 2.0/Video/HDMI/Wifi (IEEE802.11b/g/n)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: normal; text-align: left;&quot; /&